OL,5, A trial of scrapping return tickets in 
OL,6, a bid to make fares simpler will be    
OL,7, extended as part of a shake-up of the  
OL,8, country's railways.                    
OL,10,FTransport Secretary Mark Harper will   
OL,11,Fconfirm on Tuesday that publicly-owned 
OL,12,FLNER will extend its trial of selling  
OL,13,Fsingle tickets only on its routes.     
OL,15,FUnder the trial, a single is always    
OL,16,Fhalf the cost of a return. Currently,  
OL,17,Fmany singles are #1 less than a return.
OL,19,FThe government said such reforms could 
OL,20,Fprovide "better value" for passengers. 
